[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    133[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mGeneral Architecture Pattern prose:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Expand the "Post-generation validation" bullet to explicitly name the terminal state: "Failures retry with augmented prompting up to N times; retry-exhausted failures route to a distinct human-review queue (separate DynamoDB table and S3 archive) and do NOT proceed to tier/render/archive or flow to the clinician UI."[K
